      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "title: \"Day 1 - Block 4\"\n",
        "subtitle: \"Tools 1\"\n",
        "format:\n",
        "  revealjs:\n",
        "    footer: \"TI Workshop | D1 B4\"\n",
        "    bibliography: ../../../resources/workshop-citations.bib\n",
        "    embed-resources: true\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "## Tools Are the true Leap [^s2]\n",
        "\n",
        "- Agents can act externally\n",
        "- *\"World\"* responds with observations\n",
        "- New state enters context\n",
        "\n",
        "[^s2]: Sources: @yao2022react; @schick2023toolformer\n",
        "\n",
        "## Tool Calls Are Tokens [^s3]\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "```{mermaid}\n",
        "%%| fig-align: \"center\"\n",
        "sequenceDiagram\n",
        "  participant M as Model\n",
        "  participant X as Runtime\n",
        "  participant W as World\n",
        "  M->>X: tool-call tokens\n",
        "  X->>W: execute action\n",
        "  W-->>X: observation\n",
        "  X-->>M: append to context\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "[^s3]: Sources: @schick2023toolformer; @yao2022react\n",
        "\n",
        "## Ready-Made Agents: Claude Cowork [^s4]\n",
        "\n",
        "- Prebuilt orchestration and UX\n",
        "- Tooling and context integrated\n",
        "- Fast path for first workflows\n",
        "\n",
        "[^s4]: Sources: @claudePlatformDocs; @opencodeDocs\n",
        "\n",
        "## How can I give my agent tools? {.center} [^s5]\n",
        "\n",
        "[^s5]: Sources: @akersh:2024; @openaiApiDocs; @claudePlatformDocs\n",
        "\n",
        "## Model-Context Protocol: Calling Tools [^s6]\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "```{mermaid}\n",
        "%%| fig-align: \"center\"\n",
        "flowchart LR\n",
        "  A[Agent Client] --> B[MCP Server]\n",
        "  B --> C[Tool 1]\n",
        "  B --> D[Tool 2]\n",
        "  B --> E[Resource]\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "[^s6]: Sources: @opencodeDocs; @claudePlatformDocs\n",
        "\n",
        "## Agent Skills: Defining behavior\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "```{text}\n",
        "my-skill/\n",
        "├── SKILL.md          # Required: instructions + metadata\n",
        "├── scripts/          # Optional: executable code\n",
        "├── references/       # Optional: documentation\n",
        "└── assets/           # Optional: templates, resources\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "## Skills vs MCP [^s7]\n",
        "\n",
        "| MCP | Skill |\n",
        "|---|---|\n",
        "| Interface | Behavior |\n",
        "| Connect tools | Solve tasks |\n",
        "| Tool logic | Agent logic |\n",
        "\n",
        "[^s7]: Sources: @ragSkillMcpRlm; @willisonAgenticPatterns\n",
        "\n",
        "## Gallery of Use Cases [^s8]\n",
        "\n",
        "- Code execution with feedback\n",
        "- Web search with grounding\n",
        "- Chrome DevTools for web apps\n",
        "\n",
        "```python\n",
        "# Code execution expands capability\n",
        "result = run_python(\"pytest -q\")\n",
        "state.append(result)\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "[^s8]: Sources: @akersh:2024; @opencodeDocs; @claudePlatformDocs\n",
        "\n",
